						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up on the steps in front of the Chennakēśava temple.</p>						

						<p>SADĀŚIVADĒVARĀYA.</p>						

						<p>Undated.</p>						

						<p>This undated inscription can be assigned to the period of Sadāśivadēvarāya on the basis of internal evidence.</p>						

						<p>Mutilated and damaged. Registers the gifts of lands at • • • • • Dēvayapalle probably to the temple of Chennakēśvarāya.</p>						

						</summary>
